node.text:
In honor of @khabib_nurmagomedov fight week I am posting this video to show you a fun interaction of how we all look interact. Nobody is serious in this video and definitely nobody feels disrespected. Khabib actually says he would punch me but he won’t because I’m older than him... how crazy is this? Watch how @dc_mma big bro’s both of us Lol Covid sucks! It also so amazing our young wrestlers get to interact with these dudes. I miss these dudes like crazy. Just got off the phone w @islam_makhachev and I can’t wait until we can all train in the same room again. Excited to watch the legacy continue this weekend! Let’s go!

node.text:
Hey guys this is my first vlog and I wanted to do this so I could express my thoughts and feelings of the loss and so you guys could understand how I was feeling during my fight. This is a very raw and vulnerable video trying to not hide any emotion and being very transparent with you guys. I hope you enjoy. 
S/O @iamthebay for the great edits.
